 pa ću čitati ljeto.

1627
01:26:16,140 --> 01:26:16,840
 Danas mi ljudi zaustavljaju.

1628
01:26:16,840 --> 01:26:17,800
 Čitaću lošu, je li?

1629
01:26:17,800 --> 01:26:19,080
 E, čitaću lošu, tako bi.

1630
01:26:19,080 --> 01:26:20,680
 i sad me ljudi zaustavljaju,

1631
01:26:20,680 --> 01:26:22,080
 sad ovih dana,

1632
01:26:22,080 --> 01:26:23,520
 jer je to toliko aktualno,

1633
01:26:23,520 --> 01:26:24,380
 i mi kožu,

1634
01:26:24,380 --> 01:26:24,720
 admiral,

1635
01:26:24,720 --> 01:26:26,800
 pa kako ste vi mogli to,

1636
01:26:26,800 --> 01:26:30,480
 još te 2025. u svojom knjizi gospodari,

1637
01:26:30,480 --> 01:26:31,480
 kao se napisati,

1638
01:26:31,480 --> 01:26:32,720
 a to se sve sada događa.

1639
01:26:32,720 --> 01:26:35,300
 Sad ću ja onako pravo pitati,

1640
01:26:35,300 --> 01:26:35,860
 admiral,

1641
01:26:35,860 --> 01:26:37,980
 ali što onda nas čeka?

1642
01:26:37,980 --> 01:26:39,040
 Još ove godine,

1643
01:26:39,040 --> 01:26:39,580
 2025.

1644
01:26:39,580 --> 01:26:40,620
 Što nas čeka?

1645
01:26:40,620 --> 01:26:43,040
 Idemo mi malo strateški razmišljati

1646
01:26:43,040 --> 01:26:44,220
 u sljedećih 10-20 godina.

1647
01:26:44,220 --> 01:26:45,320
 Ovako, što nas čeka?

1648
01:26:45,320 --> 01:26:48,360
 Prvo, Hrvatska treba,

1649
01:26:48,360 --> 01:26:50,060
 kad je ovo manje od mjesec dana,

1650
01:26:50,060 --> 01:26:52,960
 treba riješiti svoj untarnji,

1651
01:26:52,960 --> 01:26:54,200
 determinirani kaos

1652
01:26:54,200 --> 01:26:55,420
 koje je sama proizvela.

1653
01:26:55,420 --> 01:26:56,960
 To je auntention.

1654
01:26:56,960 --> 01:26:58,440
 Nama ne treba neko iz vani,

1655
01:26:58,440 --> 01:26:59,620
 dovoljno smo mi i sami,

1656
01:26:59,620 --> 01:27:00,860
 ne treba na niko duš vani,

1657
01:27:00,860 --> 01:27:01,620
 ništa nam ne treba.

1658
01:27:02,020 --> 01:27:03,520
 Još ako se neki duš vani pojavi,

1659
01:27:03,520 --> 01:27:04,600
 još da možemo ujediniti,

1660
01:27:04,600 --> 01:27:05,960
 kao što smo u domovinskom ratu.

1661
01:27:05,960 --> 01:27:08,160
 Već zanimljivo je da je

1662
01:27:08,160 --> 01:27:09,520
 predsjednik Pilanović govorio

1663
01:27:09,520 --> 01:27:11,200
 o vladi nacionalnog jedinstva,

1664
01:27:11,200 --> 01:27:11,700
 je li tako?

1665
01:27:11,700 --> 01:27:14,360
 Vjerojatno mu je bila usporedba

1666
01:27:14,360 --> 01:27:14,760
 sa tim,

1667
01:27:14,760 --> 01:27:16,460
 1991. godina kada je bila vlada

1668
01:27:16,460 --> 01:27:17,440
 nacionalnog jedinstva,

1669
01:27:17,440 --> 01:27:18,400
 kada je Tušman.

1670
01:27:18,400 --> 01:27:20,720
 Dakle, očigledno je državo pogibjeli,

1671
01:27:20,720 --> 01:27:23,480
 ali nije toliko izvansko na agresiju,

1672
01:27:23,480 --> 01:27:24,640
 nego unutarnju.

1673
01:27:24,640 --> 01:27:26,500
 Nima unutarnju agresiju.

1674
01:27:26,500 --> 01:27:28,800
 To što je ovo u strategiji definirava.

1675
01:27:29,200 --> 01:27:30,520
 Dakle, unutarnja agresija

1676
01:27:30,520 --> 01:27:32,860
 kada su sve institucije blokirane.

1677
01:27:32,860 --> 01:27:34,700
 Danas su sve institucije blokirane.

1678
01:27:34,700 --> 01:27:35,680
 U Hrvatskoj.

1679
01:27:35,680 --> 01:27:36,380
 Ne funkcionira.

1680
01:27:36,380 --> 01:27:38,940
 Od Sabora do ovoga,

1681
01:27:38,940 --> 01:27:39,640
 kako se zove,

1682
01:27:39,640 --> 01:27:41,080
 Ustavnog suda,

1683
01:27:41,080 --> 01:27:43,120
 sada ne bram sve drugo što je ostaloga.

1684
01:27:43,120 --> 01:27:45,520
 Dakle, ako je to unutarnja agresija,

1685
01:27:45,520 --> 01:27:46,820
 ona se samo unutarnjom snagom

1686
01:27:46,820 --> 01:27:48,500
 može i prezriješiti.

1687
01:27:48,500 --> 01:27:49,960
 Niko vam ne može izvani.

1688
01:27:50,040 --> 01:27:51,200
 da je u hemahina,

1689
01:27:51,200 --> 01:27:51,760
 kao što je bilo

1690
01:27:51,760 --> 01:27:52,860
 u grčkim strategijama,

1691
01:27:52,860 --> 01:27:53,840
 u Hrvatskom slučaju

1692
01:27:53,840 --> 01:27:54,580
 ono ne vrijedi.

1693
01:27:54,580 --> 01:27:55,960
 To je jedno.

1694
01:27:55,960 --> 01:27:56,840
 Drugo,

1695
01:27:56,840 --> 01:27:58,980
 mislim da će najviše utjecati

1696
01:27:58,980 --> 01:28:00,180
 ovaj geopolitički,

1697
01:28:00,180 --> 01:28:02,480
 globalni strateški poremećaj

1698
01:28:02,480 --> 01:28:04,640
 i da ne našo zaslugo,

1699
01:28:04,640 --> 01:28:05,420
 mi ćemo se,

1700
01:28:05,420 --> 01:28:07,340
 moglo bi i našom zaslugo,

1701
01:28:07,340 --> 01:28:09,060
 onda bi tada bilo ozbiljni grači,

1702
01:28:09,060 --> 01:28:09,860
 to sam već rekao,

1703
01:28:09,860 --> 01:28:12,640
 biti na pravoj strani povijesti.

1704
01:28:13,640 --> 01:28:15,120
 Dakle, sve će ovisiti

1705
01:28:15,120 --> 01:28:16,300
 od ovih izbora

1706
01:28:16,300 --> 01:28:19,280
 za kad je 17. travnja.

1707
01:28:19,280 --> 01:28:20,560
 Dakle, od njih

1708
01:28:20,560 --> 01:28:21,380
 ko će biti?

1709
01:28:21,380 --> 01:28:27,040
 Hoće li ova briselska ekipa

1710
01:28:27,040 --> 01:28:27,980
 ostati dalje,

1711
01:28:27,980 --> 01:28:29,860
 pa uništao još malo što je ostalo?

1712
01:28:29,860 --> 01:28:32,420
 Ili će doći neka nova ekipa?

1713
01:28:32,420 --> 01:28:35,380
 Mislim, SDP nije taj

1714
01:28:35,380 --> 01:28:36,860
 koji bi on mogao promijeniti,

1715
01:28:36,860 --> 01:28:38,020
 jer on po svom habitusu

1716
01:28:38,020 --> 01:28:38,960
 ne može promijeniti

1717
01:28:38,960 --> 01:28:39,960
 ova nova vremena.

1718
01:28:39,960 --> 01:28:41,020
 A jesu li oprostite

1719
01:28:41,020 --> 01:28:41,800
 što vas prekidame?

1720
01:28:41,800 --> 01:28:43,400
 Milanović i Plenković

1721
01:28:43,400 --> 01:28:44,520
 dva lica istog

1722
01:28:44,520 --> 01:28:45,900
 globalističkog novčića.

1723
01:28:45,900 --> 01:28:47,160
 Resimo, to ima

1724
01:28:47,160 --> 01:28:47,920
 takve postavke.

1725
01:28:47,920 --> 01:28:49,120
 Ja, slušaj,

1726
01:28:49,120 --> 01:28:50,540
 ako ovo što bi ja sada rekao

1727
01:28:50,540 --> 01:28:51,240
 da bi se opredijelio

1728
01:28:51,240 --> 01:28:51,800
 za jednu stranu

1729
01:28:51,800 --> 01:28:52,360
 u ovoj emisiji,

1730
01:28:52,360 --> 01:28:53,400
 ja se ne želim opredijeliti

1731
01:28:53,400 --> 01:28:54,840
 na jednu stranu,

1732
01:28:54,840 --> 01:28:56,900
 a da ovo što govorim

1733
01:28:56,900 --> 01:28:58,400
 da dobro gledatelji odvagnu

1734
01:28:58,400 --> 01:28:59,580
 i da oni pronađu

1735
01:28:59,580 --> 01:29:00,720
 tu pravu stranu.

1736
01:29:00,720 --> 01:29:02,080
 Evo, tako ću odgovoriti.

1737
01:29:02,080 --> 01:29:02,960
 Dakle, ne želim

1738
01:29:02,960 --> 01:29:03,740
 i neću.

1739
01:29:03,740 --> 01:29:04,880
 Kao strategiju

1740
01:29:04,880 --> 01:29:05,520
 bilo bi to

1741
01:29:05,520 --> 01:29:06,320
 popuno pogrešno.

1742
01:29:06,320 --> 01:29:06,920
 Ko što sam ja

1743
01:29:06,920 --> 01:29:08,120
 nisem opredijelio

1744
01:29:08,120 --> 01:29:10,080
 u ovoj ukrajinskoj

1745
01:29:10,080 --> 01:29:10,680
 za rusku

1746
01:29:10,680 --> 01:29:12,320
 ili za bilo koju drugu stranu.

1747
01:29:12,320 --> 01:29:13,700
 To što ja govorim

1748
01:29:13,700 --> 01:29:14,500
 istinu što će biti,

1749
01:29:14,500 --> 01:29:15,440
 a to se je potvrdilo,

1750
01:29:15,440 --> 01:29:16,740
 ovaj da je.

1751
01:29:16,740 --> 01:29:17,320
 Tako, tako neću

1752
01:29:17,320 --> 01:29:18,020
 ni u ovom slučaju.

1753
01:29:19,000 --> 01:29:20,200
 ali da će ići

1754
01:29:20,200 --> 01:29:21,300
 u brzase procesi

1755
01:29:21,300 --> 01:29:22,340
 to sigurno znam.

1756
01:29:22,340 --> 01:29:26,600
 Ako pobjedi jedna strana,

1757
01:29:26,600 --> 01:29:27,660
 neimenujući drugo,

1758
01:29:27,660 --> 01:29:30,260
 tada je moguće

1759
01:29:30,260 --> 01:29:31,160
 da se nastavi

1760
01:29:31,160 --> 01:29:32,160
 ova agonija

1761
01:29:32,160 --> 01:29:34,920
 i izgubit ćemo

1762
01:29:34,920 --> 01:29:35,840
 podosta vremena.

1763
01:29:35,840 --> 01:29:38,120
 Znam ja da mene

1764
01:29:38,120 --> 01:29:38,820
 mnogi pitaju,

1765
01:29:38,820 --> 01:29:39,300
 pa dobro,

1766
01:29:39,300 --> 01:29:41,160
 ovi su bili,

1767
01:29:41,160 --> 01:29:42,260
 misli se ovo,

1768
01:29:42,260 --> 01:29:43,080
 komunizam,

1769
01:29:43,080 --> 01:29:43,800
 uvijek komunizam.

1770
01:29:43,800 --> 01:29:44,700
 Komunizam je davno,

1771
01:29:44,700 --> 01:29:45,740
 ima gore ideologije

1772
01:29:45,740 --> 01:29:46,220
 od komunizma.

1773
01:29:46,220 --> 01:29:46,600
 Rekao sam,

1774
01:29:46,600 --> 01:29:48,000
 to je militantni liberalizam,

1775
01:29:48,060 --> 01:29:49,900
 svi smo zarobljenici

1776
01:29:49,900 --> 01:29:53,360
 te antikristove ideologije.

1777
01:29:53,360 --> 01:29:54,700
 Ono je bila antikristova,

1778
01:29:54,700 --> 01:29:56,560
 a ovo je antikristova

1779
01:29:56,560 --> 01:29:57,520
 na treću potenciju.

1780
01:29:57,520 --> 01:30:00,120
 Ideologije živimo,

1781
01:30:00,120 --> 01:30:01,320
 ispranih mozgova,

1782
01:30:01,320 --> 01:30:02,200
 više ili manje.

1783
01:30:02,200 --> 01:30:03,720
 Tada će se,

1784
01:30:03,720 --> 01:30:04,780
 opet uvijek govorimo

1785
01:30:04,780 --> 01:30:05,740
 o jakos trajcijene.

1786
01:30:05,740 --> 01:30:07,600
 Ako pobjedi ona,

1787
01:30:07,600 --> 01:30:08,140
 što ja mislim

1788
01:30:08,140 --> 01:30:09,200
 da bi trebalo pobjedi,

1789
01:30:09,200 --> 01:30:11,440
 i ako se sastavi vlada

1790
01:30:11,440 --> 01:30:13,200
 koja bi bila na tragu

1791
01:30:13,200 --> 01:30:14,940
 te vlade

1792
01:30:14,940 --> 01:30:16,060
 nacionalnog jedinstva,

1793
01:30:16,060 --> 01:30:17,900
 a vladu nacionalnog jedinstva,

1794
01:30:18,720 --> 01:30:20,000
 ako žele uistiti dobro Hrvatsko,

1795
01:30:20,000 --> 01:30:21,720
 može sastaviti jedna ili druga strana

1796
01:30:21,720 --> 01:30:22,480
 ko dobije vlaste.

1797
01:30:22,480 --> 01:30:23,180
 To je ključeno.

1798
01:30:24,860 --> 01:30:27,000
 Znači treba pronaći snage

1799
01:30:27,000 --> 01:30:28,240
 koje će okrenuti,

1800
01:30:28,240 --> 01:30:30,240
 poznati umne ljude u Hrvatsko

1801
01:30:30,240 --> 01:30:31,180
 ovako i reći,

1802
01:30:31,180 --> 01:30:31,400
 ajde,

1803
01:30:31,400 --> 01:30:32,800
 zato u svakdje postoji

1804
01:30:32,800 --> 01:30:33,620
 vijeće mudraca,

1805
01:30:33,620 --> 01:30:34,740
 vijeće svijedi i glava,

1806
01:30:34,740 --> 01:30:37,080
 a to znači preko 75 godine,

1807
01:30:37,080 --> 01:30:38,900
 kada tada mudrost dolazi.

1808
01:30:38,900 --> 01:30:39,640
 Mudrost ne možeš,

1809
01:30:39,640 --> 01:30:40,320
 možeš imati znanje,

1810
01:30:40,320 --> 01:30:41,780
 ali ne znaš da imaš mudru.

1811
01:30:41,780 --> 01:30:43,280
 Sa 20 ili 30, da.

1812
01:30:43,520 --> 01:30:45,040
 Mogu okrenuti Hrvatsko

1813
01:30:45,040 --> 01:30:46,660
 i onda sjesti i raspravljati

1814
01:30:46,660 --> 01:30:47,840
 ko što mi raspravljamo

1815
01:30:47,840 --> 01:30:51,240
 u ovom ovdje emisiji vašog.

1816
01:30:51,240 --> 01:30:52,860
 Sve smo stavili na sto,

1817
01:30:52,860 --> 01:30:53,260
 evo.

1818
01:30:53,260 --> 01:30:55,600
 Ja, pitam li odgovaratel.

1819
01:30:55,600 --> 01:30:56,920
 Tako i drugi.

1820
01:30:56,920 --> 01:30:58,940
 Još je bolje kada bi sučeljavali se.

1821
01:30:58,940 --> 01:30:59,360
 Još bolje.

1822
01:30:59,360 --> 01:31:00,700
 Onda se izvirsili mnoge stvari.

1823
01:31:00,700 --> 01:31:02,860
 I to će biti za Hrvatsko.

1824
01:31:02,860 --> 01:31:04,860
 A ako to ne bude tako,

1825
01:31:04,860 --> 01:31:07,560
 onda uistinu se možemo

1826
01:31:07,560 --> 01:31:10,300
 zabrinuti za našu domovnu

1827
01:31:10,300 --> 01:31:10,980
 i naš narod,

1828
01:31:10,980 --> 01:31:12,360
 kojega je nažalost sve manje,

1829
01:31:12,360 --> 01:31:14,680
 koji je udaljio se

1830
01:31:14,680 --> 01:31:16,920
 od svojih hršćanskih katoliških korijena,

1831
01:31:16,920 --> 01:31:20,860
 u kojim je crkva prilati,

1832
01:31:20,860 --> 01:31:23,140
 crkveni, izgubljeni u prostoru i vremenu.

1833
01:31:23,140 --> 01:31:26,020
 Nažalost u Vatikanu je instaliran

1834
01:31:26,020 --> 01:31:29,920
 čovjek koji je njihov igrač

1835
01:31:29,920 --> 01:31:31,820
 ovaj okultne oligarhije.

1836
01:31:31,820 --> 01:31:33,360
 Ja mu neću reći funkciju,

1837
01:31:33,360 --> 01:31:34,260
 ne ime, najmanje.

1838
01:31:34,260 --> 01:31:37,300
 Ovaj papa zvan Buanosera,

1839
01:31:37,560 --> 01:31:40,060
 zamislite vi da on kada je dobio pontifikat,

1840
01:31:40,060 --> 01:31:41,860
 pojavi se ispred

1841
01:31:41,860 --> 01:31:45,940
 puk hršćanskog katoliškog svjetoga Petra

1842
01:31:45,940 --> 01:31:47,840
 i u mjesto juda je blagost,

1843
01:31:47,840 --> 01:31:49,080
 on kaže Buanosera.

1844
01:31:49,080 --> 01:31:51,020
 Sve je tada bilo jasno ko je on.

1845
01:31:51,020 --> 01:31:52,800
 Evo, i to je tako.

1846
01:31:52,800 --> 01:31:56,020
 I oni su se nažalost opredijelili,

1847
01:31:56,020 --> 01:31:58,480
 opredijelili se za materijalno,

1848
01:31:58,480 --> 01:31:59,340
 a ne za duhovno.

1849
01:31:59,340 --> 01:32:00,420
 Mi smo na crkvu.

1850
01:32:00,420 --> 01:32:04,020
 Pa čini je materijalno, zna se što piše tamo u Bibliji,

1851
01:32:04,020 --> 01:32:05,500
 kome služiš.

1852
01:32:05,600 --> 01:32:09,640
 Ili, Bogu Mamonu ili Bogu novca.

1853
01:32:09,640 --> 01:32:12,520
 Odnosno, Mamon se simbolizira kao novac,

1854
01:32:12,520 --> 01:32:14,760
 ali u biti je to u prijevodu točnome,

1855
01:32:14,760 --> 01:32:17,360
 znači krivo stečeno bogatstvo.

1856
01:32:17,360 --> 01:32:20,540
 Evo, to je ono, pravi prijevod bi bio,

1857
01:32:20,540 --> 01:32:21,600
 kad bi puninu riječi.

1858
01:32:22,220 --> 01:32:24,540
 Malmona, preveli se.

1859
01:32:24,540 --> 01:32:26,260
 Prima tome danas oni služe,

1860
01:32:26,260 --> 01:32:27,480
 oni se moraju vrati.

1861
01:32:27,480 --> 01:32:30,560
 Dakle, prvo crkva mora se vrati.

1862
01:32:30,560 --> 01:32:31,580
 I još ti nešto reći.

1863
01:32:31,580 --> 01:32:33,080
 Nisem nija znao.

1864
01:32:33,080 --> 01:32:35,180
 Dakle, uvijek čovjek porad sjegli,

1865
01:32:35,180 --> 01:32:36,100
 život učiti.

1866
01:32:36,100 --> 01:32:40,080
 I ovi su izmislili da se crkva u se kristije,

1867
01:32:40,080 --> 01:32:41,940
 čini se crkvu stavio u se kristije.

1868
01:32:42,420 --> 01:32:43,980
 Od francuske revolucije,

1869
01:32:43,980 --> 01:32:46,420
 zašto je propada Evropa krišćanska?

1870
01:32:46,420 --> 01:32:49,880
 Ona je dosegla vrkunac o svemu toga smo rekli.

1871
01:32:49,880 --> 01:32:54,020
 Zato jer su prvo iz kulture izbacili vjeru,

1872
01:32:54,020 --> 01:32:57,760
 pa su iz politike izbacili vjeru,

1873
01:32:57,760 --> 01:33:00,160
 pa zato je ta crkve nema.

1874
01:33:00,160 --> 01:33:01,760
 Kad ti izbaciš iz znanosti,

1875
01:33:01,760 --> 01:33:03,340
 ti si izbacili vjeru iz te tri stvari.

1876
01:33:03,340 --> 01:33:06,560
 Kad nema znanost, kultura i politika,

1877
01:33:06,560 --> 01:33:09,480
 duhovnog, ona je može biti svašta.

1878
01:33:09,480 --> 01:33:10,000
 I svačija.

1879
01:33:10,000 --> 01:33:10,860
 Što si dogodili.

1880
01:33:10,860 --> 01:33:11,540
 Dakle, bacaje.

1881
01:33:11,540 --> 01:33:12,080
 Tako je.

1882
01:33:12,420 --> 01:33:14,460
 I sad se to treba vratiti.

1883
01:33:14,460 --> 01:33:20,140
 I stoji po kanonima katoličke crkve

1884
01:33:20,140 --> 01:33:22,520
 da crkve ni prelati,

1885
01:33:22,520 --> 01:33:23,920
 ili veliko dostajanstvenici,

1886
01:33:23,920 --> 01:33:24,780
 neke države,

1887
01:33:24,780 --> 01:33:26,460
 neći manjati ni čije.

1888
01:33:26,460 --> 01:33:30,660
 Ako je ta država ugroženi ljezni interes,

1889
01:33:30,660 --> 01:33:32,080
 odnosno narod te države,

1890
01:33:32,080 --> 01:33:34,280
 vjerski i katolički,

1891
01:33:34,280 --> 01:33:38,020
 tada crkva može čak i osnivati stranke

1892
01:33:38,020 --> 01:33:41,020
 i moriti se za vlast da vrati na pravi narod.

1893
01:33:41,540 --> 01:33:45,620
 Evo, prema tome, crkva ovakva koja je pristala

1894
01:33:45,620 --> 01:33:49,260
 da nju financira iz budžeta,

1895
01:33:49,260 --> 01:33:52,180
 hrvatskoga ne je samostalna crkva.

1896
01:33:52,180 --> 01:33:55,800
 Pa tebi je svaka mlada koja god dođe,

1897
01:33:55,800 --> 01:33:57,880
 a svaka mila gora od prekode njim je dobra.

1898
01:33:57,980 --> 01:33:59,700
 jer da je novac.

1899
01:33:59,700 --> 01:34:00,740
 Tako je.

1900
01:34:00,740 --> 01:34:01,940
 Ako ste vi crkva naroda,

1901
01:34:01,940 --> 01:34:03,260
 krisova crkva u narod,

1902
01:34:03,260 --> 01:34:05,260
 narod će vas prepoznati.

1903
01:34:05,260 --> 01:34:07,740
 Narod je hrvatski velikodušan

1904
01:34:07,740 --> 01:34:09,520
 i uvijek je bio sa crkom.

1905
01:34:09,520 --> 01:34:12,460
 S tim više smo mi marijanski narod.

1906
01:34:12,460 --> 01:34:14,700
 Dakle, marijanski narod,

1907
01:34:14,700 --> 01:34:15,820
 mi pripadamo tome.

1908
01:34:15,820 --> 01:34:18,260
 Mi smo narod kojeg je svetac,

1909
01:34:18,260 --> 01:34:21,100
 Ivan Pavao II. nazvao narodom Nade.

1910
01:34:21,640 --> 01:34:23,680
 To nije nazvao ni svoj poljski narod.

1911
01:34:23,680 --> 01:34:25,160
 Mi smo ti.

1912
01:34:25,160 --> 01:34:27,700
 E pa onda budemo narod Nade.

1913
01:34:27,700 --> 01:34:29,680
 A ne narod bez nađa.

1914
01:34:29,680 --> 01:34:31,200
 Narod bez vjere.

1915
01:34:31,200 --> 01:34:33,540
 Kako mi mislimo da smo mi bez vjere katolička obstati?

1916
01:34:33,540 --> 01:34:35,320
 Pa kako su našli ostali toliko godina?

1917
01:34:35,320 --> 01:34:37,100
 Mi smo hrvatski

1918
01:34:37,100 --> 01:34:38,920
 hrvatski njim primili u prvo stoljeću.

1919
01:34:38,920 --> 01:34:41,380
 U ovim našim ilirskim,

1920
01:34:41,380 --> 01:34:42,680
 današnjim hrvatskim zemljama

1921
01:34:42,680 --> 01:34:43,580
 na koje je hodio?

1922
01:34:43,580 --> 01:34:44,740
 Sveti Pavel.

1923
01:34:44,740 --> 01:34:48,180
 On piše, ima u poslanici njegov i nima.

1924
01:34:48,180 --> 01:34:50,240
 Sveti Luka,

1925
01:34:50,240 --> 01:34:51,440
 drugi evanđelist,

1926
01:34:51,560 --> 01:34:54,080
 piše u dijelima apostolskim

1927
01:34:54,080 --> 01:34:56,480
 da je on poslao svoje najbolje učenike

1928
01:34:56,480 --> 01:34:58,600
 u zemlju Dalmaciju.

1929
01:34:58,600 --> 01:34:59,960
 Jako ste inspirirani.

1930
01:34:59,960 --> 01:35:00,680
 Sviđa mi se to.

1931
01:35:00,680 --> 01:35:02,180
 Ali ja još moram par pitanja.

1932
01:35:02,180 --> 01:35:03,240
 U, pa to je puno vezi.

1933
01:35:03,240 --> 01:35:05,060
 Nema veze, brzo ćemo mi to.

1934
01:35:05,060 --> 01:35:08,400
 Ako Ukrajini prijeti primjerice,

1935
01:35:08,400 --> 01:35:09,720
 evo, to su neka blic pitanja,

1936
01:35:09,720 --> 01:35:11,480
 čerupanje, da tako kažem.

1937
01:35:11,480 --> 01:35:14,960
 Prijeti li to čerupanje

1938
01:35:14,960 --> 01:35:17,280
 danas, sutra, možda i na Balkanu?

1939
01:35:17,280 --> 01:35:18,560
 Ovako.

1940
01:35:18,560 --> 01:35:21,480
 Procesi geopolitički sigurno

1941
01:35:21,480 --> 01:35:23,180
 onim neće više status kvokave,

1942
01:35:23,180 --> 01:35:24,440
 bilo ovo više biti neće.

1943
01:35:24,440 --> 01:35:25,240
 Nakon Ukrajinskog,

1944
01:35:25,240 --> 01:35:26,080
 posredničkog rata,

1945
01:35:26,080 --> 01:35:27,220
 ili kako Rusi zovu

1946
01:35:27,220 --> 01:35:28,100
 specialne operacije,

1947
01:35:28,100 --> 01:35:29,020
 više ništa besi,

1948
01:35:29,020 --> 01:35:30,360
 neće isto pa i tako dalje.

1949
01:35:30,360 --> 01:35:32,000
 Ta jugoistok Evrope,

1950
01:35:32,260 --> 01:35:34,940
 u knjigu se nema Balkana.

1951
01:35:34,940 --> 01:35:39,220
 Balkan je turska riječ za planinu.

1952
01:35:39,220 --> 01:35:43,540
 Bugari su pobjegli od te riječi

1953
01:35:43,540 --> 01:35:45,240
 i nešto što se može nazvati

1954
01:35:45,240 --> 01:35:47,340
 Balkan je stara planina,

1955
01:35:47,340 --> 01:35:48,620
 a mi smo ostalo,

1956
01:35:48,620 --> 01:35:50,420
 gdje narijedi su alpsko nabiranje.

1957
01:35:50,420 --> 01:35:51,040
 Ovo je stariji.

1958
01:35:51,040 --> 01:35:52,840
 Oni zovu stara planina.

1959
01:35:53,580 --> 01:35:54,980
 Balkan nije polotok.

1960
01:35:54,980 --> 01:35:56,760
 Da je polotok,

1961
01:35:56,760 --> 01:35:58,600
 onda bi ova hopnena,

1962
01:35:58,600 --> 01:36:00,000
 jer definicija polotoka

1963
01:36:00,000 --> 01:36:01,400
 bila kraća,

1964
01:36:01,400 --> 01:36:03,600
 a nije ovdje duža

1965
01:36:03,600 --> 01:36:04,800
 od ove ostale dvije.

1966
01:36:04,800 --> 01:36:05,600
 To je jedno.

1967
01:36:05,600 --> 01:36:06,420
 Polotok je,

1968
01:36:06,420 --> 01:36:08,020
 mora kroz cijeli njega

1969
01:36:08,020 --> 01:36:09,700
 imati maritimne utjecaje.

1970
01:36:09,700 --> 01:36:12,140
 Ovo ne ima maritimnih utjecaja,

1971
01:36:12,140 --> 01:36:13,240
 šta ima u sredini,

1972
01:36:13,240 --> 01:36:14,520
 tamo oko Drine,

1973
01:36:14,520 --> 01:36:15,840
 Bosne i Hercegovine,

1974
01:36:15,840 --> 01:36:17,480
 nekakvi maritimnih utjecaja,

1975
01:36:17,480 --> 01:36:17,820
 nije ima.

1976
01:36:17,920 --> 01:36:19,300
 pa preto ne možemo i polotok,

1977
01:36:19,300 --> 01:36:21,280
 pa ni ćemo po zemljopis

1978
01:36:21,280 --> 01:36:22,180
 koji se zove znanost.

1979
01:36:22,180 --> 01:36:25,640
 Kako se zove inače

1980
01:36:25,640 --> 01:36:28,240
 koji se zove Italija?

1981
01:36:28,240 --> 01:36:29,980
 Apeninski polotok.

1982
01:36:29,980 --> 01:36:30,680
 Aha, po čemu?

1983
01:36:30,680 --> 01:36:31,880
 Po Apeninima.

1984
01:36:31,880 --> 01:36:33,020
 Dobre, Pirinejski.

1985
01:36:33,020 --> 01:36:34,360
 Isto po Pirinejima.

1986
01:36:34,360 --> 01:36:35,400
 Isto i Skandinavski.

1987
01:36:35,400 --> 01:36:37,400
 Pa na tome da je polotok,

1988
01:36:37,400 --> 01:36:37,840
 a nije,

1989
01:36:37,840 --> 01:36:40,060
 onda se ovo ne može zovati Balkan,

1990
01:36:40,060 --> 01:36:41,420
 nego bi se,

1991
01:36:41,420 --> 01:36:42,040
 kako je zvao,

1992
01:36:42,040 --> 01:36:42,660
 Dinarik.

1993
01:36:42,660 --> 01:36:44,280
 I ja ga u svojom knjizi

1994
01:36:44,280 --> 01:36:45,740
 zovem Dinarik.

1995
01:36:45,740 --> 01:36:46,680
 Po Dinarik.

1996
01:36:46,920 --> 01:36:48,480
 E, dakle,

1997
01:36:48,480 --> 01:36:50,620
 i to smo raštisili,

1998
01:36:50,620 --> 01:36:51,280
 ova šta ima.

1999
01:36:51,280 --> 01:36:51,840
 Može.

2000
01:36:51,840 --> 01:36:52,820
 Zašto?

2001
01:36:52,820 --> 01:36:55,720
 A glavno izvorište je

2002
01:36:55,720 --> 01:36:58,000
 stvaranje velike Albanije.

2003
01:36:58,000 --> 01:37:00,180
 A veliku Alban,

2004
01:37:00,180 --> 01:37:01,560
 to je američki plan,

2005
01:37:01,560 --> 01:37:02,760
 isključivo američki,

2006
01:37:02,760 --> 01:37:04,220
 dakle, nema Evropa s tim.

2007
01:37:04,220 --> 01:37:05,940
 Zato se gradi sada,

2008
01:37:05,940 --> 01:37:06,700
 pored tiranije,

2009
01:37:06,700 --> 01:37:08,560
 tamo velika baza.

2010
01:37:08,560 --> 01:37:10,540
 A velika baza,

2011
01:37:10,540 --> 01:37:11,420
 gdje je napravljena,

2012
01:37:11,420 --> 01:37:13,760
 99. godine nakon toga,

2013
01:37:13,760 --> 01:37:14,880
 nakon bombardiranja,

2014
01:37:14,880 --> 01:37:16,560
 je u bolj stilu,

2015
01:37:16,560 --> 01:37:17,260
 u Oroševcu,

2016
01:37:17,260 --> 01:37:18,340
 na Kosovu.

2017
01:37:18,340 --> 01:37:18,980
 Dakle, Kosovu.

2018
01:37:18,980 --> 01:37:20,160
 Zašto je ona tu napravljena?

2019
01:37:20,160 --> 01:37:22,940
 Zato jer je ona na sredini

2020
01:37:22,940 --> 01:37:24,620
 između Crnog mora i Jadrana.

2021
01:37:24,620 --> 01:37:26,220
 A Jadrana na sredini

2022
01:37:26,220 --> 01:37:27,360
 u sredozemljeg mora

2023
01:37:27,360 --> 01:37:28,480
 da se može kontrolirati.

2024
01:37:28,480 --> 01:37:28,960
 Inače,

2025
01:37:28,960 --> 01:37:30,820
 jedna je u geostrategiji

2026
01:37:30,820 --> 01:37:31,480
 zanimljivost,

2027
01:37:31,480 --> 01:37:32,600
 kada se uzme u šestar

2028
01:37:32,600 --> 01:37:33,820
 i opisa se kružnica

2029
01:37:33,820 --> 01:37:35,920
 od Moskve do Teherana,

2030
01:37:36,740 --> 01:37:38,640
 u kilometar je jednaka udaljenost.

2031
01:37:38,640 --> 01:37:40,480
 Ništa nije,

2032
01:37:40,480 --> 01:37:41,560
 je matematika.

2033
01:37:41,560 --> 01:37:42,440
 Ništa nije slučajno.

2034
01:37:42,440 --> 01:37:43,820
 Ništa, matematika je čista,

2035
01:37:43,820 --> 01:37:46,540
 luluja je čista matematika,

2036
01:37:46,540 --> 01:37:47,360
 teorija skupova,

2037
01:37:47,360 --> 01:37:48,240
 to je uvjerojatno

2038
01:37:48,240 --> 01:37:49,560
 sad je nevana i teorija igala,

2039
01:37:49,560 --> 01:37:50,900
 ali da je sad ne zamarastim.

2040
01:37:50,900 --> 01:37:52,200
 Dakle, to je.

2041
01:37:52,200 --> 01:37:54,020
 A ta velika Albanija

2042
01:37:54,020 --> 01:37:54,880
 je bila Albanija,

2043
01:37:54,880 --> 01:37:56,180
 bila Kosovo,

2044
01:37:56,180 --> 01:37:58,200
 jedna trećina

2045
01:37:58,200 --> 01:37:59,940
 zapadna Makedonija,

2046
01:38:00,740 --> 01:38:01,860
 ove dvije općine

2047
01:38:01,860 --> 01:38:03,720
 Bujanovac i Preševo u Srbiji,

2048
01:38:03,720 --> 01:38:05,340
 jedan dio Crne Gore,

2049
01:38:05,340 --> 01:38:07,740
 čak jedan manji dio Grške.

2050
01:38:07,740 --> 01:38:09,440
 To bila Albanija,

2051
01:38:09,440 --> 01:38:12,280
 koja bi po njihovim zasadama,

2052
01:38:12,280 --> 01:38:13,800
 američkim,

2053
01:38:13,800 --> 01:38:16,780
 bila dovoljno kompaktna cijelina

2054
01:38:16,780 --> 01:38:17,960
 da jedne strane

2055
01:38:17,960 --> 01:38:19,580
 zaustavi projekciju

2056
01:38:19,580 --> 01:38:20,600
 nakon Ukrajine,

2057
01:38:20,600 --> 01:38:22,500
 projekciju moći Rusije

2058
01:38:22,500 --> 01:38:24,620
 prema sredini sredozemlja,

2059
01:38:24,620 --> 01:38:26,520
 zato smo je Hrvatska bitna.

2060
01:38:26,520 --> 01:38:28,920
 Jer smo jedna od četiri

2061
01:38:28,920 --> 01:38:30,620
 gravitacijske stožerne

2062
01:38:30,620 --> 01:38:31,840
 točke Evrope,

2063
01:38:31,840 --> 01:38:34,820
 a takvih ima samo 17 u svijetu,

2064
01:38:34,820 --> 01:38:35,940
 četiri u Evropi.

2065
01:38:35,940 --> 01:38:37,220
 I za moji gledatelji

2066
01:38:37,220 --> 01:38:37,820
 da znaju,

2067
01:38:37,820 --> 01:38:38,980
 ovo je geostrategija

2068
01:38:38,980 --> 01:38:39,760
 najviše razine.

2069
01:38:39,760 --> 01:38:41,460
 Te četiri točke su

2070
01:38:41,460 --> 01:38:42,600
 La Manche,

2071
01:38:42,600 --> 01:38:43,960
 Gibratar,

2072
01:38:43,960 --> 01:38:45,400
 Bospor,

2073
01:38:45,400 --> 01:38:45,920
 Daneli,

2074
01:38:45,920 --> 01:38:47,560
 Otrant i Jadran.

2075
01:38:47,560 --> 01:38:48,660
 Ko drži

2076
01:38:48,660 --> 01:38:50,600
 dvije trećine Jadrana?

2077
01:38:50,600 --> 01:38:51,120
 Hrvati,

2078
01:38:51,120 --> 01:38:52,180
 ne talijan nego mi.

2079
01:38:52,180 --> 01:38:55,440
 Oni jesu na uglazu Otranta,

2080
01:38:55,440 --> 01:38:56,580
 s druge strane Albanija.

2081
01:38:56,580 --> 01:38:57,140
 Albanija, da.

2082
01:38:57,140 --> 01:38:58,020
 Ali je bitno Jadran,

2083
01:38:58,020 --> 01:38:59,140
 jer kao more

2084
01:38:59,140 --> 01:39:00,440
 koje se najviše ulači

2085
01:39:00,500 --> 01:39:01,640
 u Evropsko kopno.

2086
01:39:01,640 --> 01:39:04,380
 I zato sve od Skandinavije

2087
01:39:04,380 --> 01:39:05,520
 i Središnje Evrope,

2088
01:39:05,520 --> 01:39:06,760
 Hrvatska je još jedno

2089
01:39:06,760 --> 01:39:08,220
 po geostratečkih zasadama,

2090
01:39:08,220 --> 01:39:08,720
 ovih ne znam,

2091
01:39:08,720 --> 01:39:09,760
 to bi svaki učenik

2092
01:39:09,760 --> 01:39:10,540
 ne može izići

2093
01:39:10,540 --> 01:39:12,080
 iz razreda bilo kojega

2094
01:39:12,080 --> 01:39:12,800
 od osnovne škole

2095
01:39:12,800 --> 01:39:13,980
 da ovo ne zna šta ću reći.

2096
01:39:13,980 --> 01:39:16,380
 Hrvatska je jedina zemlja

2097
01:39:16,380 --> 01:39:17,040
 u Evropi

2098
01:39:17,040 --> 01:39:18,060
 koja je isto dobno

2099
01:39:18,060 --> 01:39:19,100
 srednjoevropska

2100
01:39:19,100 --> 01:39:21,200
 i srednozemna zemlja.

2101
01:39:21,200 --> 01:39:22,180
 Jedina, nemate druge.

2102
01:39:22,180 --> 01:39:23,160
 To smo učili, da.

2103
01:39:23,160 --> 01:39:24,000
 Bar nekada.

2104
01:39:24,000 --> 01:39:25,400
 To ti govori vrijedno

2105
01:39:25,400 --> 01:39:26,380
 zašto se svi bore

2106
01:39:26,380 --> 01:39:27,720
 ti sve ne pojel.

2107
01:39:27,720 --> 01:39:28,940
 Zašto je Hrvatska važna

2108
01:39:28,940 --> 01:39:30,240
 pa i za rusku geopolitiku

2109
01:39:30,240 --> 01:39:30,940
 a ne Srbije?

2110
01:39:30,940 --> 01:39:32,160
 Iz ovih razloga što sam sada.

2111
01:39:32,160 --> 01:39:33,720
 Ja moguće čarupanje Hrvatske?

2112
01:39:33,720 --> 01:39:34,960
 Malo prije ste rekli...

2113
01:39:34,960 --> 01:39:36,020
 Ne, ne, ne, čarupanje.

2114
01:39:36,020 --> 01:39:37,360
 Šta više se može očarupati

2115
01:39:37,360 --> 01:39:37,940
 u Hrvatske?

2116
01:39:37,940 --> 01:39:39,120
 Više nema šta očarupati.

2117
01:39:39,120 --> 01:39:40,080
 Rekao se ono što ima.

2118
01:39:40,080 --> 01:39:41,920
 Možemo jedino razgovarati

2119
01:39:41,920 --> 01:39:42,560
 da mi govorimo

2120
01:39:42,560 --> 01:39:44,520
 o objedinjenju Hrvatske zemlja.

2121
01:39:44,520 --> 01:39:45,040
 O tome da?

2122
01:39:45,040 --> 01:39:45,820
 Aha, znači imamo

2123
01:39:45,820 --> 01:39:45,920
 veće pove dobro.

2124
01:39:45,920 --> 01:39:47,500
 Ne, čarupanje, više nema.

2125
01:39:47,500 --> 01:39:48,900
 Nemaš više šta očarupati?

2126
01:39:48,900 --> 01:39:49,900
 Malo prije ste rekli

2127
01:39:49,900 --> 01:39:50,780
 kako je 30%...

2128
01:39:50,780 --> 01:39:51,880
 Šta očarupati kada resimo

2129
01:39:51,880 --> 01:39:53,080
 doli kod Ljute

2130
01:39:53,080 --> 01:39:54,560
 iza Dubrovnika u Konovala?

2131
01:39:54,680 --> 01:39:56,080
 Znate koliko je udalje od zračne lidije?

2132
01:39:56,080 --> 01:39:56,880
 800 metara.

